  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">As discussed below you may opt out of third party tracking on the Service at any time However we do not currently support any browser based Do Not Track DNT settings or participate in any DNT frameworks and we do not assign any meaning to any potential DNT track signals you may send or alter any of our data collection or use practices in response to such signals</evidence>
